32
00:01:19.870 --> 00:01:22.120
Everybody's straighten up, please.

33
00:01:22.120 --> 00:01:26.760
The last secretary got fired after crossing the line, so don't think that your pretty

34
00:01:26.760 --> 00:01:38.180
face is going to get you very far with Mr. Croft.

35
00:01:38.180 --> 00:01:48.659
Afternoon, Mr. Croft.

36
00:01:48.659 --> 00:01:53.900
Are you trying to seduce your way into a promotion by throwing yourself all over Mr. Croft like

37
00:01:53.900 --> 00:01:54.900
that?

38
00:01:54.900 --> 00:01:55.900
Wow.

39
00:01:55.900 --> 00:01:57.060
Wait.

40
00:01:57.060 --> 00:01:58.060
You.

41
00:01:58.060 --> 00:01:59.060
I'm sorry.

42
00:01:59.060 --> 00:02:00.060
Mr. Croft.

43
00:02:00.060 --> 00:02:01.780
This is the new secretary, Elise.

44
00:02:01.780 --> 00:02:02.780
Yeah.

45
00:02:02.780 --> 00:02:06.659
Hey, Ellie.

46
00:02:06.659 --> 00:02:08.520
Good heart.

47
00:02:08.520 --> 00:02:16.800
I forgot to tell you that my best friend, Elise, just started working at your company.

48
00:02:16.800 --> 00:02:18.960
