49
00:02:18.960 --> 00:02:19.960
She's your best friend.

50
00:02:19.960 --> 00:02:22.789
He's got a total copycat.

51
00:02:22.789 --> 00:02:28.229
She's always tried to take my stunts and she applied to work for you after I told

52
00:02:28.229 --> 00:02:29.229
her about us.

53
00:02:29.229 --> 00:02:31.939
Well, I'd keep my distance from her if I were you.

54
00:02:31.939 --> 00:02:32.939
Yeah.

55
00:02:32.939 --> 00:02:33.939
Don't worry.

56
00:02:33.939 --> 00:02:37.740
I won't allow someone like that in my company.

57
00:02:37.740 --> 00:02:38.740
Mr. Croft.

58
00:02:38.740 --> 00:02:39.740
I didn't mean it.

59
00:02:39.740 --> 00:02:40.740
Hey, Andy.

60
00:02:40.740 --> 00:02:42.740
I want you to take her to HR, fire her immediately.

